(1, 1, '2015-03-23 10:20:56', '2015-03-23 10:20:56', 'Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!', 'Hello world!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hello-world', '', '', '2015-03-23 10:20:56', '2015-03-23 10:20:56', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(2, 1, '2015-03-23 10:20:56', '2015-03-23 10:20:56', 'As most of you are probably aware, Prem Chiruvolu has decided to relinquish his executive position in Nigeria. Deepak Singhal will succeed him and take over his role as CEO of a set of the Group’s entities, namely, Multipro (and its subsidiaries),\r\n\r\nLucky Fibres and V-Connect (in addition to his current role as CEO of Dufil). Prem will however continue to act as an Advisor on Group-related matters in 2014. We rely on his experience and counsel to assist the growth of the Group in years to come. We wish to thank Prem for his impactful leadership since 2000. We also wish Deepak all the best as he assumes his new responsibilities.\r\n\r\nHe can, I’m sure, count on all of us for the same level of support that was extended to Prem.\r\n\r\nSajen Aswani\r\n\r\nChief Executive', 'Tolaram Intranet', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sample-page', '', '', '2015-03-23 10:49:43', '2015-03-23 10:49:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
